After having, among other things, fully re-developed the test engine and the user interface (see version 2.0.3 "what's new"), this new version resolve a few bugs newly discovered, including:

- a crash when trying to save a test result picture in the photo library (with the "share" option at the end of a test)
- a crash arriving a very few times on the cancelation or the timeout of the browse test
- some minor bugs especially due to the speed test threaded connexions management

After having, among other things, fully re-developed the test engine and the user interface (see versions 2.3.x "what's new"), this new version resolve a few bugs newly discovered, including:

- a buffer issue on the upload test for Wifi « low » bitrate connexions
- a display issue of the type and the country flag of test servers on a full test result
- a display issue on the Premium subscription expiration date
- some minor bugs
